# The image bakes only the dependency set (plus the tiny provider-registration shim,
# see Dockerfile). DAGs/plugins are mounted at runtime, so keep the build context to
# pyproject.toml + uv.lock + provider_registration/ (fast, reproducible, no local junk).
*
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!provider_registration
!provider_registration/**
provider_registration/**/__pycache__
